company.name: Cycle System
company.description:
Cycle gives access to energy, to entire communities, through a smart system of renewable energy that in turn is profitable for the householder.  

Our decentralised system consists of a smart network of off-the-grid houses with renewable sources installed. The hardware is installed in entire communities. The Harvester, our IoT (Internet of Things) device, integrates Artificial Intelligence, which allows the household to boost the energy generation potential; in order to create an energy surplus. 

The Harvester knows who has a surplus of energy, who needs energy, and let it flow through the network. All transactions are secured on a Blockchain, and the household who shares its energy instantly receives a monetary compensation for it, creating a reliable and scalable peer to peer energy trading system that turns houses into productive units.
